task.summary: Default task

Switching over to IntelliJ.
Also going to try to switch to Expandablelistview. ListView has been giving me a ton of issues.
Also, using IntelliJ's built-in git support as opposed to the cli like normal. Also on Windows. So this commit might be effed up.
Added list deleting.
Added list renaming.
Added custom background support. Was surprisingly easy!
Am going to try to get a market-ready version.
Fixed the date dialog size & location
Added the progressbar for auth.

Forgot about committing again.
More steps toward Version2. UI is just about done-ish, minus tweaks that the other guys want done.
Now, the hard part: sync.
Fixed an issue with it not showing the correct views on group expand/collapse.
Added ability for checkmarks to toggle the priority indicator

Actually made it where if you check an item it gets checked in the dbase.
I swear to god, if I actually missed this and it didn't accidentally get taken out in the changeover....

Fixed sorting with finished tasks
Now they are always on the bottom: if you sort or if you don't.

Started sync work. NOTE: BROKEN BUILD.
(I realize it's not proper to make a commit where the app is broken, but I need to push my changes to save them for the night.)
This is mostly the sync.coffee file ported to Java. But there are parts I don't quite understand yet, so I left those parts in Coffeescript as markers.
I also left some comments at the bottom of SyncHelper_v2 about what I believe still needs to be done. A talk with George will hopefully clear it up.

Did some work on the Classic compatibility.
Finally fixed the coloring for selecting a list.
Finally fixed Ubuntu One sync.
Finished tasks now show up in their respective lists.

Fixed the "day starts on" for >ICS.
I think, haven't had a chance to test it.
Fixed the name not being updated until you exit a list and re-enter it.
Fixed where other rows would show the Edit Name field when scrolling.
Better animations.
Fixed views not always displaying right for no tags
Fixed issue 22
Preparing to finally release an update to the app store.

1.5 release!
Added a bunch of locales. Tweaked the splash & about. Added a Donate button in the options.

Fixed some minor issues
Fixed a crash when trying to show the New List dialog more than once Fixed a crash when pressing the menu button while the splash is showing
Fixed the date being displayed wonky on the button
Fixed the "time until" not being displayed correctly.
Hopefully fixed the spinner not being set to the right date when editing an existing task.
Both "All Tasks" and "Today" should have their totals updated when you add/delete or edit the date, respectively
Fixed some shit with the themes, mostly not being readable b/c there are no transparent backgrounds behind text
Made background tileable
Added the Blue Coffee theme.

Fixed ability to add tasks to Today and Next.
Today should also now show tasks that are overdue but not done.
Added ability to move things into the logbook.
Updated the license and the Readme
Added colors for things like "days overdue"
Trying to get search working

Added ability to search.
Hit the search key. If you are in a certain list, it will search just that list, if you are at "All Lists" or at the lists screen, it will search all.
It currently searches for title, notes, and tags.
